          "date": "2012-01-06 09:18:35.000000000",
          "tz": -480
        },
        "subject": "LU-952 quota: follow locking order of quota code",
        "message": "LU-952 quota: follow locking order of quota code\n\nThe locking order of quota code is: i_mutex > dqonoff_sem >\njournal_lock > dqptr_sem > dquot->dq_lock > dqio_mutex, so we\nshould call the ll_vfs_dq_init() after journal started to avoid\ndeadlock.\n\nSigned-off-by: Niu Yawei <niu@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ia88a2eb8c9dc3827afd4828e0160ee376a1f041e\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
